The paper discusses the integration of software model checking techniques into the DevOps culture, which is a software engineering practice. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of regression tests and the integration of formal verification techniques into the developer workflow, which are related to programming languages (cs.PL) and logic (cs.LO). The paper also mentions the scalability and adaptability of software model checking, which is related to systems and control (cs.SY).
